quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  11,24,"Emikanda chibili echo chili shinga omuwofu nende owekala amarwi, nende owulolanga nende owulilanga, koo babili abo bakhayelana toto? Shimuparangakhwo tawe"
  11,25,Ne toto khwaruma Nuhu khubandu bebe. (Nababoolela) “Toto esie endi Omwikanyilisi wenyu Owahabulafu.”
  11,26,"Mulalaama halali Nyasaye butswa (yenyene), esie abaririra eshinyasio shie inyanga indulu"
  11,27,"Abakhongo babakhayi mubandu bebe nibaboola mbu; “Efwe shikhukhulolanga noli shiosi shiosi tawe, oli butswa Omundu shinga efwe, ne shikhukhulolanga halali abalondi bao nibo abateshele mwifwe, bakhulondelekhwo khuliparo liokhuchaka, ne shikhubalolanga nimukhushilila shiosishiosi tawe, halali khubaparira mbu muli ababeyi"
  11,28,"Yaboola;”Enywe Abandu banje, mulola murie nendi nende eshimanyisio okhurula khu Nyasaye wanje, neyambelesiye tsimbabaasi okhurula khuye, mana mwesi tsiboolele, koo khwakhabanichilisia okhutsichama nanyu ni mukhayile"
  11,29,"Ne enywe Abandu banje, esie shebenyaangakhwo omwandu tawe, omurungo kwanje kulibuswa khu Nyasaye, ne esie shindakhatafia balia abasuubila tawe, toto bo balibukanana nende Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, halali esie ebalolanga enywe nimuli Abandu balamanyile tawe"
  11,30,"Enywe Abandu banje! Wina witsa okhuhabina imbeli wa Nyasaye, nikali mbu ebatafia abo? Shimuparangakhwo tawe"
  11,31,"Ne shebaboolelanga mbu endi nende ebiachi bia Nyasaye tawe, nohomba mbu esie ndamanya amakhuwa kefisile, nohomba shemboola mbu “esie endi Malaika tawe” nohomba shemboola mbu: “balia abababusinjiamwo tsimoni mbu Nyasaye shalabahelesia obulayi tawe.” Nyasaye niye umanyile muno akali mumioyo chiabu(nemboola endio) Toto nditsa okhuba mubandu abamabii"
  11,32,"Baboola mbu: “ewe Nuhu, wakhalomaloma ninafuu muno, ne oburirisiye amakhuwa muno, mana nakharera akokhulakanga ako toto noli owuboolanga obwatoto.”"
  11,33,"Naboola mbu; “Nyasaye alabarerera niyenya, ne enywe shimunyala okhumushila tawe”"
  11,34,"Ne amachelo kanje khwinywe shikakhakhonya tawe, nindenya okhubachelela, Nyasaye niyenya okhubalekha mukore, Ye niye Omulesi wenyu, na ni ewuwe ni wamulikalusibwa"
  11,35,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu; “Yakasiasa omwene” boola mbu;” Nendi ndakakasia tsimbii tsilikhwisie, nasi endi ehale nende amabii kamukholanga.”"
  11,36,"Nuhu nafimbulilwa mbu: “ toto abulaho witsa okhusubila mubandu bawo halali balia bamala okhusuubila, kho alabeelela khukabakholanga tawe.”"
  11,37,"Ne okasie iriaro (safina) mutsimoni tsiefu, nende khubufimbuli bwefu, ne olanomianomia amakhuwa kabandu ababii tawe, toto abo betsa okhufwa okhurulana nende amatsi"
  11,38,"Ne nachaka okhukasia obwaro(isafina), ne buli Abandu be nibabura bamutseshelelanga, naye yaboolanga mbu; “nimukhutseshelela, fwesi khulabatseshelela\tshingala mukhutseshelelanga.”"
  11,39,"Ne mwitsa okhumanya wina ulanyoola eshinyasio shio khumututuyia, ne wina witsa okhwishilibwa eshinyasio shilawa"
  11,40,"Olwa likhuwa liefu liola, mana liloba nilichaka okhubitikha amaatsi, khwamuboolela mbu; “injisiamwo (muliaro) eshisatsa neshikhasi, nende Abandu bawo- halali balia belikhuwa liamala okhubura- nende abasuubila, ne shibasuubila halala ninaye halali batiti"